reference:
  ICAP Functions [deprecated]
  ICAP




    &reftitle.intro;


      Icap will be removed in near future. Neither this module, nor
      those versions of icap library are supported any longer. If you
      want to use calendar capabilities in PHP, use mcal instead.






    &reftitle.required;


      The icap library has to be installed, which is not longer supported and available.





    &reftitle.install;


     To get these functions to work, you have to compile PHP with
     --with-icap.





    &reftitle.runtime;
    &no.config;




    &reftitle.resources;
    &no.resource;




    &reftitle.constants;
    &no.constants;



